    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i dont really have time to go to a clinic right now, it's so expensive and the wait is always crazy here. if i just use the lubricant drops and maybe some warm compresses, won't that eventually clear it up if it's just irritation? i really don't want to deal with an eye doctor unless it gets way worse.",
