      "content": "wait, you can just get antibiotic drops over the counter at a pharmacy without a prescription? i didn't know that. i saw some drops at the shop earlier that looked like they could help with infections, but i wasn't sure if they were safe to just use on my own. which kind of drops should i be looking for specifically so i don't waste my money?",
